trans-unit.source: Identifies the types of connection points that a transformer supports.
trans-unit.target: 변환기에서 지 원하는 연결 지점의 유형을 식별 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Transformers are used to translate data between two Web Parts controls with incompatible connection points.
trans-unit.target: 변환기는 호환 되지 않는 연결 지점과 두 개의 웹 파트 컨트롤 간의 데이터를 변환 하는 데 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Connection points are incompatible when they provide or consume data through different interfaces.
trans-unit.target: 연결 지점을 제공 하거나 다른 인터페이스를 통해 데이터를 사용 하는 경우 호환 되지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, a provider implementing a provider connection point of type <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow> could not directly connect to a consumer expecting a provider connection point of type <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartTable>.
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어, 형식 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow>공급자 연결 지점 이름 필드에 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartTable>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartTable> 의 기대 하는 소비자에 직접 연결할 수</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow> 의 공급자 연결 지점을 구현 하는 공급자

trans-unit.source: Instead, a transformer must be used to connect the two connection points.
trans-unit.target: 대신 두 개의 연결 요소를 연결 하는 변환기를 사용 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A customized transformer can be created by deriving a class from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>클래스</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> 에서 클래스를 파생 하 여 사용자 지정된 변환기를 만들 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartTransformerAttribute attribute is applied to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
It defines the type of provider connection point and the type of consumer connection point that a transformer supports.
trans-unit.target: 공급자 연결 지점 유형과 변환기에서 지 원하는 소비자 연결 지점의 유형을 정의 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The type of consumer and provider connection points supported by the transformer must match the connection points of the consumer and provider Web Parts controls for a connection to be made between the controls.
trans-unit.target: 변환기에서 지 원하는 공급자 및 소비자 연결 지점의 유형을 컨트롤 간에 만들어지는 연결에 대 한 소비자 및 공급자 웹 파트 컨트롤의 연결점 일치 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: At run time, the type of connection points that a particular transformer supports can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetProviderType%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: 실행 시 특정 변환기에서 지 원하는 연결 지점의 유형을 통해 검색할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A>및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetProviderType%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetProviderType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute"></xref> class.
The WebPartTransformerAttribute constructor sets the consumer connection point type and the provider connection point type for the transformer.
trans-unit.target: WebPartTransformerAttribute 생성자 변환기에 대 한 소비자 연결 지점 유형 및 공급자 연결 지점 형식을 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: These values can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ConsumerType%2A> property and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ProviderType%2A> property, respectively.
trans-unit.target: 이러한 값을 통해 검색할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ConsumerType%2A>속성 및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ProviderType%2A>속성을 각각.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ProviderType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ConsumerType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the interface supported by the consumer connection point.
The <xref:System.Type> of the interface supported by the provider connection point.
consumerType or providerType is not specified.
consumerType equals providerType.
Gets the <xref:System.Type> of the interface supported by the consumer connection point.
trans-unit.target: 가져옵니다는 <xref:System.Type>소비자 연결 지점에서 지원 되는 인터페이스입니다.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The ConsumerType property is set through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
The <xref:System.Type> of the interface supported by the consumer connection point.
Returns the consumer type a transformer can accept on a connection point.
trans-unit.target: 소비자 형식 변환기 연결 지점에서 받아들일 수 있는 반환 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> object and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object use the GetConsumerType method to determine whether the consumer type of the transformer matches the consumer connection point of the Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>개체 및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>개체 변환기의 소비자 형식이 있는 소비자 연결 지점 웹 파트 컨트롤의과 일치 하는지 확인 하려면 GetConsumerType 메서드를 사용 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The type of transformer.
The <xref:System.Type> of the consumer connection point.
transformerType is not specified.
transformerType is not an object derived from the class.
Returns the provider type a transformer can accept on a connection point.
trans-unit.target: 공급자 유형 변환기는 연결 지점에서 받아들일 수 있는 반환 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> object and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object use the GetProviderType method to determine whether the provider type of the transformer matches the provider connection point of the Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>개체 및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>공급자 유형 변환기의 웹 파트 컨트롤의 공급자 연결 지점 일치 하는지 확인 하려면 GetProviderType 메서드를 사용 하는 개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

The <xref:System.Type> of the provider connection point.
transformerType is not specified.

Gets the <xref:System.Type> of the interface supported by the provider connection point.
trans-unit.target: 가져옵니다는 <xref:System.Type>공급자 연결 지점에서 지원 되는 인터페이스입니다.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The ProviderType property is set through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
The <xref:System.Type> of the interface supported by the provider connection point.
